extends base

block content
  div(class="row")
    div(class="col-md-12")

      div
        h3 Sorry, something went wrong serving your request

        p Swingletree may be missing a mandatory resource (for example a database connection) and can therefore not serve you the web interface.

        p Please try again later or message your Swingletree administrator.

        if error
          hr
          div(style="font-size:.7em")
            p(style="font-weight:bold") It's dangerous to go alone! Take this.
            pre=error.stack